high_descs: Turn around and go to the living room.
There is the book on the pink colored table.
Take the book and go to the next room.
Place the book near the lamp and it will be glow.
anns.task_desc: Glow the lamp using the book.

high_descs: Turn to your left, move straight, turn to your right, walk straight, then turn to your left towards the pink table
Pick up the book on the table
Turn to your left, walk ahead, then turn to your right,  head straight towards the big lamp in the corner of the bed
Turn on the big lamp in the corner of the bed
anns.task_desc: Examine the book by the big lamp in the corner

high_descs: Turn left and walk down the corridor, turn around a large sofa to the right and walk beside the middle of it, then turn left and approach a table.
Pick up a lamp remote from the table.
Turn left and walk straight towards the entrance on the right, enter the room and walk to the lamp.
Turn on the lamp with the lamp remote.
anns.task_desc: Use a remote to turn the lamp on

high_descs: Turn and head toward the tvstand in the study table.
Pick the book from the study table.
Head toward the wall then turn right to reach the bed room and go straight to reach the table. See the floorlamp in the corner.
Turn on the floorlamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a book by the light of a tall FloorLamp.

high_descs: Turn left and walk through the balcony to reach the living room, turn right and stand facing the tvstand.
Pick up the book from the table.
Turn left and walk then turn right to enter into the bedroom, stand facing the floorlamp.
Turn on the floorlamp and examine the book in the lamp light.
anns.task_desc: Find the book and go to the bedroom to exam in the book in the floorlamp light
